{"tid":2206377,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"錫林浩特市稱民族語言授課4校近3500學生全部到校","createTime":"2020-09-17T12:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T12:26:00.000Z","uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8585f9c74611c681c5e019a0b72fe70bd57afc1a","tid":2206377,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:20:16.000Z","msg":"內蒙古錫林浩特市表示，截至今日早上9時，以民族語言授課的3間小學及1間中學，近3500名學生全部到校，各學校全面恢復正常教學秩序。<br />\n<br />\n錫市前日發公告，指在昨日規定時間內按時送子女入學的家長，在各類項目和扶持政策上給予傾斜，否則會追究法律責任，子女則會取消學籍及資助等。<br />\n<br />\n錫市所屬的錫林郭勒盟昨日亦發公告指，會將有關家長納入失信人員名單和採取「聯合懲戒」，包括限制從事特定行業、乘坐火車和飛機、住宿賓館飯店和高消費旅遊等。<br />\n<br />\n內蒙古上月底要求學校，新學年起在3個科目改用國家統編課程及漢語授課後，引發罷課、示威和抗議。"},{"pid":"3d5272f5a96387490932d61ab9be40a8050b5612","tid":2206377,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/talk/page/800/2020/09/09/phpEbslia.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Ftalk%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F09%2F09%2FphpEbslia.jpg&h=a306b313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://botanwang.com/sites/default/files/field/image/2020-03-27T201951Z_2048483331_RC2KSF9EBKHC_RTRMADP_3_BRAZIL-POLITICS-PROTEST_2.jpg?itok=du0PrEvf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbotanwang.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Ffield%2Fimage%2F2020-03-27T201951Z_2048483331_RC2KSF9EBKHC_RTRMADP_3_BRAZIL-POLITICS-PROTEST_2.jpg%3Fitok%3Ddu0PrEvf&h=da6d9d49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5769097969d88284b0f03aaa1ffc9a4e23410bd4","tid":2206377,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T12:26:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">以民族語言授課的</span><br />\n唔用普通話先有高返校率"}]}